00:48:58.541 --> 00:48:59.833
Do-yeon.

00:49:01.335 --> 00:49:02.336
Apa maksud awak?

00:49:02.419 --> 00:49:04.588
Saya menyapanya di tadika tadi.

00:49:05.297 --> 00:49:06.882
Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

00:49:07.132 --> 00:49:08.759
Saya tak jumpa dia kat mana-mana.

00:49:10.427 --> 00:49:11.262
Saya akan datang segera.

00:49:24.567 --> 00:49:26.235
Ia seseorang yang Do-yeon kenali.

00:49:26.318 --> 00:49:27.528
Do-yeon...

00:49:27.611 --> 00:49:30.948
Bolehkah kami periksa rakaman keselamatan
yang menghadap jalan raya?

00:49:31.031 --> 00:49:32.116
Oh, ya.

00:49:38.706 --> 00:49:39.540
Olivia.

00:49:41.125 --> 00:49:43.711
