00:53:46.954 --> 00:53:48.038
Jangan risau, Cik Jung.

00:53:49.414 --> 00:53:50.457
Teruskan memaklumkan kami.

00:53:50.749 --> 00:53:52.292
Jangan risau, Nam-yeon.

